Building:

Cross-build for ARM:
cd build
export ARM_TOOLCHAIN_PATH=<your ARM toolchain root path>
<<e.g. export ARM_TOOLCHAIN_PATH=/work/ARM-toolcahin/oe/>>
make -f makefile-ARM clean all

For x86
cd build
make -f makefile-x86 clean all

Running:
to run the binary enter ./modbus_json <URL>
<<e.g ./modbus_json http/myserver.com>>

Set the following environement variables before building to controll the modbus and http post part (any or both can be set):

export USE_DUMMY_HTTP=1 will disable the http post and redirect JSON to stdout
export USE_DUMMY_MODBUS=1 will disable the modbus communication and use dummy data


 
